race.description: Selangor Turf Club Trophy Maiden Plate
race.comment: JUST WALTER (1) looked a run short placing here first-up before coming back and missing a nose from the front stepping up to this trip. He has the inside gate and can control the race again. Rates clear and should be winning. SAMURAI WAND (3) was much better beaten 1.7L in the same race. Keeps the 1.5kg claim and with the extra fitness can get closer. LIFE OF TREE (2) has been knocking on door on the turf and has his first try on a poly track. He races forward and expect the surface to suit. Has a 1.5 kg claim and should get every chance. RISE AND RESIST (8) resumed on the turf at the Sunshine Coast and placed second beaten 8.5L behind Vovo. Presents fitter and the in-form Lloyd is booked. Should enjoy the longer trip and also deserves plenty of consideration.
